{"id": "art-410", "label": "Art. 410", "title": "Art. 410: Întocmirea dosarului profesional", "slug": "art-410", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 410: Întocmirea dosarului profesional </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)În scopul asigur&#259;rii\neviden&#355;ei func&#355;ionarilor publici în cadrul autorit&#259;&#355;ilor\n&#351;i institu&#355;iilor publice se întocme&#351;te dosarul profesional\npentru fiecare func&#355;ionar public.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_735100300\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1317\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_735100300\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>1</sup>)În scopul realiz&#259;rii eviden&#355;ei\n&#351;i managementului func&#355;iei publice &#351;i al func&#355;ionarilor\npublici, Agen&#355;ia Na&#355;ional&#259; a Func&#355;ionarilor Publici\nprime&#351;te datele &#351;i informa&#355;iile necesare din dosarele\nprofesionale ale func&#355;ionarilor publici din cadrul autorit&#259;&#355;ilor\n&#351;i institu&#355;iilor publice.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1546811758\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1316\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1546811758\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>2</sup>)În aplicarea prevederilor alin. (1<sup>1</sup>),\nAgen&#355;ia Na&#355;ional&#259; a Func&#355;ionarilor Publici utilizeaz&#259;\ninstrumente informatice la care autorit&#259;&#355;ile &#351;i\ninstitu&#355;iile publice au acces în condi&#355;iile reglementate prin\nhot&#259;rârea Guvernului prev&#259;zut&#259; la art. 411 alin. (10).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1614756597\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1315\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1614756597\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>3</sup>)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În\naplicarea prevederilor alin. (1<sup>1</sup>) &#351;i (1<sup>2</sup>), fiecare\ninstitu&#355;ie sau autoritate public&#259; transmite Agen&#355;iei\nNa&#355;ionale a Func&#355;ionarilor Publici datele de identificare a\nfiec&#259;rei autorit&#259;&#355;i &#351;i institu&#355;ii publice, precum\n&#351;i urm&#259;toarele documente &#351;i informa&#355;ii din dosarul\nprofesional al func&#355;ionarului public:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2145966463\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1314\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2145966463\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)datele de identificare a fiec&#259;rei\nautorit&#259;&#355;i &#351;i institu&#355;ii publice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_145515462\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1313\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_145515462\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)date de identificare ale func&#355;ionarilor publici;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1160928648\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1312\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1160928648\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)date &#351;i informa&#355;ii cu privire la fiecare post;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_192250842\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1311\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_192250842\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)documentele &#351;i/sau informa&#355;iile care dovedesc\nîndeplinirea de c&#259;tre func&#355;ionarii publici a condi&#355;iilor\nprev&#259;zute la art. 465;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1506027038\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1310\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1506027038\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)actele administrative privind numirea, modificarea,\nsuspendarea &#351;i încetarea raporturilor de serviciu, actele administrative\nde sanc&#355;ionare disciplinar&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_201549593\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1309\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_201549593\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)fi&#351;a postului aprobat&#259; de conduc&#259;torul\nautorit&#259;&#355;ii sau institu&#355;iei publice pentru func&#355;ia\npublic&#259; ocupat&#259; de func&#355;ionarul public;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_796384418\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1308\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_796384418\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)actele administrative prin care se stabile&#351;te sau se\nmodific&#259;, dup&#259; caz, venitul salarial definit în conformitate cu\nprevederile din legisla&#355;ia-cadru privind salarizarea personalului\npl&#259;tit din fonduri publice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_938501330\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1307\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_938501330\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)rapoartele de evaluare a performan&#355;elor profesionale\nindividuale ale func&#355;ionarilor publici.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1445990304\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1306\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1445990304\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>4</sup>)Documentele &#351;i informa&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1<sup>3</sup>) se detaliaz&#259; prin hot&#259;rârea\nGuvernului prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (2).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_592406090\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1305\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_592406090\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>5</sup>)Documentele &#351;i informa&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1<sup>3</sup>) lit. a), d)-f) se transmit în termen de\nmaximum 10 zile lucr&#259;toare de la data emiterii actului administrativ de\nnumire în func&#355;ia public&#259;, la intrarea în corpul func&#355;ionarilor\npublici, sau de la data actului administrativ de modificare a raportului de\nserviciu în condi&#355;iile art. 505-509. Documentele &#351;i informa&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1<sup>3</sup>) lit. b), c), g) &#351;i h) se transmit\nîn termen de maximum 10 zile lucr&#259;toare de la data emiterii acestora,\nrespectiv de la data modific&#259;rii acestora, dup&#259; caz.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1961066158\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1304\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1961066158\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>6</sup>)Documentele &#351;i informa&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1<sup>3</sup>) &#351;i (1<sup>5</sup>) se transmit\nprin intermediul instrumentelor informatice prev&#259;zute la alin. (1<sup>2</sup>),\ngestionate de Agen&#355;ia Na&#355;ional&#259; a Func&#355;ionarilor Publici\npotrivit prevederilor art. 401 alin. (1) lit. d) &#351;i i).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1255501665\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1303\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1255501665\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>7</sup>)Institu&#355;iile publice din sistemul de\nap&#259;rare, ordine public&#259; &#351;i siguran&#355;&#259;\nna&#355;ional&#259; se excepteaz&#259; de la obliga&#355;ia de a transmite\ndocumentele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1<sup>3</sup>) lit. g), în condi&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1<sup>5</sup>) &#351;i (1<sup>6</sup>).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Con&#355;inutul &#351;i\nmodalitatea de gestionare a dosarului profesional se stabilesc prin\nhot&#259;râre a Guvernului, la propunerea Agen&#355;iei Na&#355;ionale a\nFunc&#355;ionarilor Publici.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Autorit&#259;&#355;ile &#351;i\ninstitu&#355;iile publice r&#259;spund de întocmirea &#351;i actualizarea\ndosarelor profesionale &#351;i asigur&#259; p&#259;strarea acestora în\ncondi&#355;ii de siguran&#355;&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)În cazurile de transfer sau de\nîncetare a raporturilor de serviciu, autoritatea sau institu&#355;ia\npublic&#259; p&#259;streaz&#259; o copie a dosarului profesional &#351;i\nînmâneaz&#259; originalul func&#355;ionarului public, pe baz&#259; de semn&#259;tur&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(5)Persoanele care au acces la\ndatele cuprinse în eviden&#355;a na&#355;ional&#259; a func&#355;iilor publice\n&#351;i a func&#355;ionarilor publici, precum &#351;i la dosarul profesional al\nfunc&#355;ionarului public au obliga&#355;ia de a p&#259;stra confiden&#355;ialitatea\ndatelor cu caracter personal, în condi&#355;iile legii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(6)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Autoritatea sau institu&#355;ia public&#259; este obligat&#259; s&#259;\nelibereze o adeverin&#355;&#259;, conform modelului prev&#259;zut la art. 137\nlit. e) din anexa nr. 10, care s&#259; ateste perioada de activitate\ndesf&#259;&#351;urat&#259; de fiecare func&#355;ionar public din cadrul\nacesteia, vechimea în munc&#259;, în specialitatea studiilor &#351;i în grad\nprofesional, în urm&#259;toarele situa&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)la\nsolicitarea func&#355;ionarului public;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)la\nmodificarea definitiv&#259; &#351;i la încetarea raportului de serviciu al\nfunc&#355;ionarului public, în condi&#355;iile legii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)în\nalte cazuri expres prev&#259;zute de lege.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_221474792\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1302\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_221474792\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6<sup>1</sup>)Func&#355;ionarii publici au acces la\ndocumentele &#351;i informa&#355;iile privind istoricul carierei individuale a\nacestora, precum &#351;i la o serie de servicii specifice online prin\ninstrumente informatice puse la dispozi&#355;ie de c&#259;tre Agen&#355;ia\nNa&#355;ional&#259; a Func&#355;ionarilor Publici.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(7)[textul din Art. 410, alin. (7)\ndin partea VI, titlul II, capitolul IV, sectiunea 3 a fost abrogat la\n28-dec-2023 de </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Art. I, punctul 15. din\nOrdonanta urgenta 121/2023</span><span style='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 4:Eviden&#355;a personalului\npl&#259;tit din fonduri publice. Sistemul electronic na&#355;ional de\neviden&#355;&#259; a ocup&#259;rii în sectorul public</span></b></p>"}